Method Detail

initialize

int initialize(java.lang.String cfgFile)
               throws IETException
Initializes IET, loads IE engines according to config file. Call this once prior to all other methods. This call is synchronous.

Parameters:
cfgFile - filepath to the IET config file.
Returns:
number of initialized IE engines.
Throws:
IETException

uninitialize

void uninitialize()
                  throws IETException
Deallocates all extraction engines. Terminates any running extraction tasks. This call is synchronous.

Throws:
IETException
